page.settings.onlinePersistence.title: Online persistence
page.settings.onlinePersistence.descript:
There are two ways to save data on tilloh.dev.
You can see the current status at the top center of each page.

üì¥ Local: If you want to use tilloh.dev in a browser on exactly one device, you don't need to do anything else.
Attention: Resetting the browser data will result in the loss of all tilloh.dev data!

üåê Cloud: Is that too insecure for you? Do you want to use your data on multiple devices? Then log in now!

page.unoSort.title: Sorting rules
page.unoSort.rules:
1. color cards are sorted according to the number in your hand, the color with the fewest cards is on the far left.
2. color cards are sorted in ascending order within the color according to their value.
3. colors with the same number of cards are sorted according to their total value.
4. black cards are always held on the far right.
